      "text": "False, 0, \"\", {}, [], (), None -> these are counted as False\n\na = [1, 2, 4, 5, False, True]\n>>> a.remove(False)\n>>> \n>>> a\n[1, 2, 4, 5, True]\n>>> a.remove(True)\n>>> a\n[2, 4, 5, True]\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
